420→      // Stop the change event from triggering save back to storage momentarily if needed
421→      // But handleChange uses the *current* storageKey from closure or ref?
422→      // handleChange depends on [storageKey], so it should be updated.
423→      // react-ace might fire onChange synchronously during setValue.
424→      // If it does, 'handleChange' will be called.
425→      // It will use the NEW storageKey.
426→      // It will save 'savedValue' to 'storageKey'.
427→      // This is redundant but harmless (saving what we just loaded).
428→
429→      editorRef.current.setValue(savedValue);
430→      editorRef.current.clearSelection();
431→      editorRef.current.focus();
432→
433→      // Update completers based on language
